@0 = ~Isn't there a policy in the taverns against walking around with a weapon out?~
@1 = ~Please put that away, <PRO_SIRMAAM>. It makes me nervous.~
@2 = ~What's that smell? It's like... bear dung, or something...~
@3 = ~NP: Who is this with us? New? Have you all decided to move out of Neverwinter now?~ /*More <PRO_RACE> folk, is it? What, did you all decide to up and leave Neverwinter, now?*/
@4 = ~I don't have time to talk to the likes of you, sorry. You could be one of them werewolves around here, for all I know.~
@5 = ~It's a good thing the plague in Neverwinter is over. If it went on any longer, the city would be too weak and there'd be war for sure!~
@6 = ~You'd best be careful on the roads. We gots werewolves in these parts... and I hear there's monster bandits all over the northern routes.~
@7 = ~Pleased to meet you, <PRO_SIRMAAM>. Don't remember seeing you in Port Llast before now.~
@8 = ~NP: I don't think I have any chance. what will you buy me a drink, buddy?~ /*I don't suppose there's a chance you'd buy me a drink, handsome?*/
